projectInfo.description:
This is part of a collaboration between Ramani Huria and GreenWastePro to tag buildings and use the process for collecting trash and revenue from waste producers in Kisutu ward, Dar es Salaam Tanzania 


The area is pretty well mapped by the then Bing imagery and other available aerial imagery. This task focuses on aligning the already mapped buildings and roads with the recent aerial imagery (to be provided by your supervisor). Please make sure every building is traced and add any that miss.

[Tracing Guide](https://gist.github.com/emilyeros/5e955ef00d9e2173d1e8).
projectInfo.instructions: Using JOSM? Please use the dedicated [preset](http://tasks.hotosm.org/project/1345/preset)
